column5: Hi what garmin map are you guys running that are fishing pine falls and traverse bay thanks

Not familar with the lakes you mentioned. I have the Garmin Ontario Inland Lake chip. If you can give me a hint where these lakes are, I could see if they are on the chip and possibly take a screen shot.
He is referring to the Winnipeg River at Pine Falls Manitoba and Traverse Bay on Lake Winnipeg, both in Manitoba.
